{"type":"champion","format":"standAloneComplex","version":"4.17.1","data":{"Khazix":{"id":"Khazix","key":"121","name":"虚空掠夺者","title":"卡兹克","image":{"full":"Khazix.png","sprite":"champion1.png","group":"champion","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48},"skins":[{"id":"121000","num":0,"name":"default"},{"id":"121001","num":1,"name":"霸天异形 卡兹克"},{"id":"121002","num":2,"name":"圣金甲虫 卡兹克"}],"lore":"一头来自虚空、名为卡兹克的恶毒掠食者渗入了瓦洛兰，准备吞噬这块大陆上最有潜力的生物们。每次猎杀后，他都会吸收掉猎物的力量，让自己进化得更加强大。卡兹克最渴望征服和吞噬的对象是雷恩加尔，一只与他实力在伯仲之间的野兽。<br><br>当卡兹克刚刚穿越到这个世界时，他非常地脆弱和饥饿。他最先遇到的一批动物实在是太弱小了，难以为他的快速进化提供给养。于是，卡兹克将他的目光转移到他所能找到的最为危险的生物上，即便冒着生命危险，也要满足进化所需的给养。每次击杀都让他大快朵颐，焕然一新，变成更强更快的掠食者。很快，卡兹克便开始用无止境的掠食欲来追杀他的猎物，并相信他已经无人能挡。一天，当他正在享用新鲜的猎物时，不幸被黄雀在后了。从遮蔽物后扑出来一只带着獠牙和铁器的生物，猛地将他按在地上。它当着他的面咆哮，又撕又抓，而卡兹克第一次感到他的血喷洒了出来。伴随着愤怒的狂啸，他划破了这头畜生的一只眼睛作为还击。他们从日落战到日出。最后，奄奄一息的他们才不情愿地分开。在他的伤口愈合后，卡兹克开始为吞噬掉这个实力堪比与虚空生物的猎物的想法所煎熬。他重新开始用加倍精力来研究这强大的猎物。终有一日，卡兹克会将雷恩加尔大卸八块，好好品尝。<br><br>“杀掉。吃掉。吸收掉。”——卡兹克","blurb":"一头来自虚空、名为卡兹克的恶毒掠食者渗入了瓦洛兰，准备吞噬这块大陆上最有潜力的生物们。每次猎杀后，他都会吸收掉猎物的力量，让自己进化得更加强大。卡兹克最渴望征服和吞噬的对象是雷恩加尔，一只与他实力在伯仲之间的野兽。<br><br>当卡兹克刚刚穿越到这个世界时，他非常地脆弱和饥饿。他最先遇到的一批动物实在是太弱小了，难以为他的快速进化提供给养。于是，卡兹克将他的目光转移到他所能找到的最为危险的生物上，即便冒着生命危险，也要满足进化所需的给养。每次击杀都让他大快朵颐，焕然一新，变成更强更快的掠食者。...","allytips":["- 在身旁一段距离内没有任何友军的敌人可以被视为孤立无援。【Q品尝恐惧】会显著提升对这些目标的伤害。","- 【无形恐惧】会在卡兹克不被敌方队伍看见时激活。可以利用草丛或者【R虚空来袭】重复激活它。别忘了用普通攻击来给敌方英雄施加【无形恐惧】的效果。","- 卡兹克在选择作战地点和作战时机方面有着极大的自由。谨慎地参加团战，从而获取胜利。"],"enemytips":["- 【Q品尝恐惧】会对孤立无援的目标造成额外伤害。在友军小兵，英雄或防御塔附近战斗，以获取优势。","- 【E跃击】和【R虚空来袭】的冷却时间很长。在它们尚未冷却完毕时，卡兹克的逃生能力会大减。"],"tags":["Assassin","Fighter"],"partype":"Mana","info":{"attack":9,"defense":4,"magic":3,"difficulty":6},"stats":{"hp":430.0,"hpperlevel":85.0,"mp":260.0,"mpperlevel":40.0,"movespeed":350.0,"armor":19.0,"armorperlevel":3.0,"spellblock":30.0,"spellblockperlevel":1.25,"attackrange":125.0,"hpregen":6.25,"hpregenperlevel":0.75,"mpregen":6.75,"mpregenperlevel":0.5,"crit":0.0,"critperlevel":0.0,"attackdamage":50.0,"attackdamageperlevel":3.1,"attackspeedoffset":-0.065,"attackspeedperlevel":2.7},"spells":[{"id":"KhazixQ","name":"品尝恐惧","description":"卡兹克会被动地标记那些与附近友军孤立的敌人。品尝恐惧会对单个目标造成物理伤害。对孤立无援的目标造成的伤害会提高。如果他选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化扩张利爪</span>的话，这个技能会对孤立无援的敌人造成额外伤害。卡兹克也会提升他的普通攻击和品尝恐惧的距离。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被动：</span>标记那些与附近友军孤立的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主动：</span>造成{{ e1 }}<span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>物理伤害。如果目标孤立无援，伤害值会提升至{{ e6 }}<span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ a2 }})</span>。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化扩张利爪：</span>如果目标孤立无援，那么伤害会提升至{{ f3 }} <span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ f2 }})</span>。【Q品尝恐惧】和卡兹克的攻击距离提升{{ e5 }}。","leveltip":{"label":["基础伤害"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5,3.5],"cooldownBurn":"3.5","cost":[25,25,25,25,25],"costBurn":"25","effect":[null,[70,95,120,145,170],[30,30,30,30,30],null,[100,100,100,100,100],[50,50,50,50,50],[91,124,156,189,221]],"effectBurn":[null,"70/95/120/145/170","30",null,"100","50","91/124/156/189/221"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.2,"key":"a1"},{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.56,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[325,325,325,325,325],"rangeBurn":"325","image":{"full":"KhazixQ.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":240,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixQ0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 法力"},{"id":"KhazixW","name":"虚空突刺","description":"卡兹克发射爆炸性的尖刺，对附近的所有敌人造成物理伤害。卡兹克如果在爆炸范围内，则会回复生命值。如果他选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化刺鞘</span>的话，虚空突刺会呈锥形发射三个尖刺，并且虚空尖刺的减速效果会得到提升。","tooltip":"发射爆炸性的尖刺，对附近的所有敌人造成{{ e1 }}<span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>物理伤害（对野怪造成20%额外伤害）和 {{ e3 }}% 的减速效果，减速持续 {{ e4 }} 秒。如果卡兹克处在爆炸范围内，则会回复 {{ e2 }}<span class=\"color99FF99\">(+{{ a2 }})</span>点生命值。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化刺鞘：</span>虚空突刺会呈锥形发射三个尖刺，并使敌人减速{{ e5 }}%，持续{{ e4 }}秒。如果命中了敌方英雄，那么卡兹克会获得这些英雄的视野（对潜行单位无效），持续2秒。","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","生命回复","法力消耗"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ e2 }} -> {{ e2NL }}","{{ cost }} -> {{ costnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[8,8,8,8,8],"cooldownBurn":"8","cost":[55,60,65,70,75],"costBurn":"55/60/65/70/75","effect":[null,[75,115,155,195,235],[40,70,100,130,160],[20,20,20,20,20],[2,2,2,2,2],[50,50,50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"75/115/155/195/235","40/70/100/130/160","20","2","50"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":1.0,"key":"a1"},{"link":"spelldamage","coeff":0.5,"key":"a2"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[1000,1000,1000,1000,1000],"rangeBurn":"1000","image":{"full":"KhazixW.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":288,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixW0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 法力"},{"id":"KhazixE","name":"跃击","description":"卡兹克跳向一个区域，在着陆时造成物理伤害。如果他选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化虫翼</span>的话，跃击的距离会得到显著提升。并且击杀和助攻将会重置跃击的冷却时间。 ","tooltip":"卡兹克跳向一个区域，在着陆时造成 {{ e1 }}<span class=\"colorFF8C00\">(+{{ a1 }})</span>物理伤害。<br><br>如果他选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化虫翼</span>的话，跃击的距离会得到显著提升。并且击杀和助攻将会重置跃击的冷却时间。 ","leveltip":{"label":["伤害","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e1 }} -> {{ e1NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":5,"cooldown":[20,18,16,14,12],"cooldownBurn":"20/18/16/14/12","cost":[50,50,50,50,50],"costBurn":"50","effect":[null,[65,100,135,170,205],[30,35,40,45,50],[10,10,10,10,10],[2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5,2.5]],"effectBurn":[null,"65/100/135/170/205","30/35/40/45/50","10","2.5"],"vars":[{"link":"bonusattackdamage","coeff":0.2,"key":"a1"}],"costType":"Mana","range":[600,600,600,600,600],"rangeBurn":"600","image":{"full":"KhazixE.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":336,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixE0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":432,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 法力"},{"id":"KhazixR","name":"虚空来袭","description":"允许卡兹克进化他的一项技能，给予它们独特的附加效果。在激活虚空来袭时，会使卡兹克潜行并触发无形威胁，同时提升移动速度。如果他选择<span class=\"color00DD33\">进化动态伪装</span>的话，虚空来袭能够施放三次，并延长潜行状态的持续时间。","tooltip":"<span class=\"colorFF9900\">被动：</span>提升虚空来袭的等级，会允许卡兹克进化他的技能。<br><br><span class=\"colorFF9900\">主动：</span>潜行{{ e1 }}秒。激活无形威胁，提升卡兹克{{ e3 }}%的移动速度，并使卡兹克能够无视单位的碰撞体积。虚空来袭能在{{ e2 }}秒内施放第二次。<br><br><span class=\"color00DD33\">进化动态伪装：</span>虚空来袭可以施放三次，并且它的持续时间延长至{{ e4 }}秒。","leveltip":{"label":["可用的进化","冷却时间"],"effect":["{{ e5 }} -> {{ e5NL }}","{{ cooldown }} -> {{ cooldownnNL }}"]},"maxrank":3,"cooldown":[100,90,80],"cooldownBurn":"100/90/80","cost":[100,100,100],"costBurn":"100","effect":[null,[1,1,1],[15,15,15],[40,40,40],[2,2,2],[1,2,3],[50,50,50]],"effectBurn":[null,"1","15","40","2","1/2/3","50"],"vars":[],"costType":"Mana","range":"self","rangeBurn":"self","image":{"full":"KhazixR.png","sprite":"spell4.png","group":"spell","x":384,"y":96,"w":48,"h":48},"altimages":[{"full":"KhazixR0.png","sprite":"spell12.png","group":"spell","x":0,"y":144,"w":48,"h":48}],"resource":"{{ cost }} 法力"}],"passive":{"name":"无形威胁","description":"当卡兹克没有在敌方队伍的视野内时，他会获得无形威胁，使他的下次对敌方英雄发动的普通攻击会造成额外的魔法伤害和减速效果。","image":{"full":"Khazix_P.png","sprite":"passive1.png","group":"passive","x":96,"y":48,"w":48,"h":48}},"recommended":[{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ASCENSION","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1036","count":2},{"id":"2003","count":3}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"type":"offensive","items":[{"id":"3078","count":1},{"id":"3071","count":1},{"id":"3181","count":1}]},{"type":"defensive","items":[{"id":"3156","count":1},{"id":"3068","count":1},{"id":"3110","count":1}]},{"type":"Consumables","items":[{"id":"2003","count":1},{"id":"2004","count":1}]}]},{"champion":"Khazix","title":"KhazixDM","type":"riot","map":"8","mode":"ODIN","priority":false,"blocks":[{"type":"starting","items":[{"id":"1001","count":1},{"id":"1036","count":2},{"id":"2003","count":3}]},{"type":"essential","items":[{"id":"3158","count":1},{"id":"3057","count":1},{"id":"3134","count":1}]},{"typ